OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781194282
OL,3,CRyanair investigated over charging
OL,4,Cparents to sit with children
OL,6,FRyanair is being investigated by the
OL,7,FUK's competition regulator over
OL,8,Fcharging parents to sit with their
OL,9,Fchildren on the budget airline's
OL,10,Fflights.
OL,12,FThe Competition and Markets Authority
OL,13,F(CMA) said it will determine whether
OL,14,Fthe practice is "in line with consumer
OL,15,Flaw".
OL,26,@vD@QOUwD@DO]
