OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781194282
OL,3,CRyanair investigated over charging
OL,4,Cparents to sit with children
OL,6,FRyanair requires at least one parent
OL,7,Fto sit with their children aged
OL,8,Fbetween two and 11, and ensures this
OL,9,Fthrough what the carrier calls a
OL,10,Fmandatory family set, typically
OL,11,Fcosting #8 each way, the CMA said.
OL,13,FPaying to reserve a seat is optional
OL,14,Ffor other passengers.
OL,16,FThe CMA said it is investigating
OL,17,Fwhether Ryanair's approach means
OL,18,F"parents are being charged for the
OL,19,Fairline to meet its child safety and
OL,20,Fdisability-related obligations as set
OL,21,Fout under aviation rules".
OL,26,@zD@AOU}D@YO]
