CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781194282
OL,3,CRyanair investigated over charging
OL,4,Cparents to sit with children
OL,6,FRyanair is "the only major airline
OL,7,Fflying out of the UK to impose this
OL,8,Fcharge", according to the watchdog.
OL,10,FOther carriers offer to seat children
OL,11,Fflying with a parent without the need
OL,12,Ffor a paid reservation, or
OL,13,Fautomatically allocate seats together
OL,14,Fduring booking, the CMA said.
OL,26,@nD@LOUpD@GO]
