OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781194282
OL,3,CRyanair investigated over charging
OL,4,Cparents to sit with children
OL,6,FThe investigation will also examine
OL,7,Fwhether Ryanair's mandatory family
OL,8,Fseat fee is a form of "drip pricing",
OL,9,Fwhich is when a business does not
OL,10,Freveal all unavoidable charges upfront
OL,11,F` only revealing them much later in
OL,12,Fthe checkout process.
OL,14,FThis practice was banned under a new
OL,15,Flaw that came into effect in April
OL,16,Flast year, although the CMA said it is
OL,17,Fat the beginning of its investigation
OL,18,Fand has "reached no conclusions about
OL,19,Fwhether Ryanair has broken the law".
OL,26,@zD@IOU{D@cO]
