OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781194282
OL,3,CRyanair investigated over charging
OL,4,Cparents to sit with children
OL,6,FHayley Fletcher, senior director of
OL,7,Fconsumer protection at the CMA, said:
OL,8,F"Lots of families save up to afford a
OL,9,Fsummer holiday and we know that extra
OL,10,Fcharges can quickly bump up the price.
OL,12,F"Our investigation will consider
OL,13,FRyanair's approach to family seat
OL,14,Freservations and how the cost is
OL,15,Fpresented to consumers, to determine
OL,16,Fwhether they comply with consumer law.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
