CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781194282
OL,3,CRyanair investigated over charging
OL,4,Cparents to sit with children
OL,6,F"For the past year, we've told
OL,7,Fbusinesses to ensure their customers
OL,8,Fare shown the total price upfront `
OL,9,Fthose who don't face the very real
OL,10,Fpossibility of action from the CMA."
