OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781194282
OL,3,CRyanair investigated over charging
OL,4,Cparents to sit with children
OL,6,FDescribing the CMA's investigation as
OL,7,F"bogus", a Ryanair spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Ryanair's family seating policy fully
OL,9,Fcomplies with all relevant laws and
OL,10,Fregulations and saves families money
OL,11,Fwhen travelling on the UK's lowest
OL,12,Ffare airline.
OL,14,F"Ryanair DOES NOT charge any fee for
OL,15,Fchildren to sit beside their parent or
OL,16,Faccompanying adult.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
