OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781194282
OL,3,CRyanair investigated over charging
OL,4,Cparents to sit with children
OL,6,F"Like all adults who select a reserved
OL,7,Fseat, adults travelling with children
OL,8,Fpay one reserved seat fee, but can
OL,9,Fselect reserved seats beside them for
OL,10,Fup to four children on the same
OL,11,Fbooking FREE OF CHARGE.
OL,13,F"This means that parents travelling
OL,14,Fwith children pay for only one (adult)
OL,15,Freserved seat but pay nothing for the
OL,16,Ffour other reserved seats for their
OL,17,Fchildren travelling with them."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
